headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Market Expansion
content: Your office is knee-deep in dollar bills and your warehouses are brimming with special cargo. So, are you ready to retire? Not just yet; you’re extremely greedy. CEOs across Los Santos now have a new frontier of illicit profiteering to explore: dominating the city’s trade in misplaced luxury vehicles is going to require every ounce of ambition and ruthlessness you can muster.
